# 5. High-Level Architecture

The completed system follows the architecture below.

```
                        User
                          │
                          ▼
                    Flask Web UI
                          │
                          ▼
                     server.py
                          │
                          ▼
                      agent.py
                          │
                          ▼
                 Google ADK Runner
                          │
                          ▼
                  Gemini 2.5 Flash
                          │
          ┌───────────────┼────────────────┐
          │               │                │
          ▼               ▼                ▼
     Tavily MCP     Google Maps MCP   Scholarship MCP
                                              │
                                              ▼
                                      Filesystem MCP
```

The Gemini model is responsible for reasoning.

The MCP servers are responsible for execution.

This separation between reasoning and execution is one of the key architectural principles demonstrated by this project.

